casebody.data:
Lavon M. BROCKMAN, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Glen R. RUBY and Lori A. Ruby, Defendants-Appellees. No. 18-0170 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

LaVon Brockman appeals the dismissal of her equitable action to abate a private nuisance and establish a drainage easement. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
